(1974, 1, '2016-08-31 04:59:20', '2016-08-31 04:59:20', '&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>partnership with school</li>\n</ul>\nSelection of schools is the first process to select students for the Sadbhaw Scholarship.A program is then conducted in the selected schools formally having an agreement with them.\n<ul>\n 	<li>forms collection/distribution</li>\n</ul>\nAfter the conduction of programme,the Sadbhaw scholarships forms are distributed in the schools.The students are made aware of the scholarships by sticking the information paper in the information board.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>First step for the selection</li>\n</ul>\nNormally,the applications for the scholarships are more than what is needed.Therefore,selections are made on the applications.This way,in the selection process priority are given to the students according to their background.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>first interview</li>\n</ul>\nTo select the capable studdents for the scholarship,a small meeting is held between the local people.To select the students,the family background,economic condition and other information about the student is taken.\n<ul>\n 	<li>final selection</li>\n</ul>\nKnowing the status and giving the interest of the student in his/her studies,the deserving students get the scholarship.The interest of the student in his/her studies,their presence in the class are given priority for their selection.Generally,students are selected on the various basis of academic background,their attendance marking up to 4500 and economic and family background rated up to 5500 for the final selection.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>distribution of scholarship</li>\n</ul>\nThe studdents selected in the first step now conduct a meeting and scholarships are given to them.DEO,CDO and other people are invited.These people encourage the people to study well and do good in the scholarship programme.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Ranking</li>\n</ul>\nThe students obtaining scholarship should maintain their ranks.The help they receive are based according to the improvements they make.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Progress Detail</li>\n 	<li>Depending upon the progress in their studies after obtaining the scholarship,the institution or the group that are handing over the scholarship to the students are made available twice a year.Criterias for the selection</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Students for Sadbhaw scholarship are selected on the basis of their educational calibre and their financial background.Any student having the chance of obtaining scholarship is based on 75% of their family background and 25% of his/her educational status at present.There are various criterias for the selection of students for sadbhaw scholarship.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Financial condition: The family background of any student obtaining the scholarship and the financial status of the family is rated first.For this type of rating,each local intellectual as well as elite organize a small independent meeting-Sadbhaw meeting is held.</li>\n</ul>\n2.Educational Qualification:For obtaining the Sadbhaw scholarship,the student should be doing well in their previous class.\n\n3.After obtaining the scholarship,the students with the scholarship must follow the rules and regulations well in order to continue the up coming years.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>InfoGraphic Image</strong>\n\n&nbsp;', 'Selection Process', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1826-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-08-31 04:59:20', '2016-08-31 04:59:20', '', 1826, 'http://localhost/sadbhaw/1826-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1975, 1, '2016-08-31 04:58:18', '2016-08-31 04:58:18', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>partnership with school</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSelection of schools is the first process to select students for the Sadbhaw Scholarship.A program is then conducted in the selected schools formally having an agreement with them.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>forms collection/distribution</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAfter the conduction of programme,the Sadbhaw scholarships forms are distributed in the schools.The students are made aware of the scholarships by sticking the information paper in the information board.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>First step for the selection</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNormally,the applications for the scholarships are more than what is needed.Therefore,selections are made on the applications.This way,in the selection process priority are given to the students according to their background.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>first interview</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTo select the capable studdents for the scholarship,a small meeting is held between the local people.To select the students,the family background,economic condition and other information about the student is taken.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>final selection</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKnowing the status and giving the interest of the student in his/her studies,the deserving students get the scholarship.The interest of the student in his/her studies,their presence in the class are given priority for their selection.Generally,students are selected on the various basis of academic background,their attendance marking up to 4500 and economic and family background rated up to 5500 for the final selection.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>distribution of scholarship</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe studdents selected in the first step now conduct a meeting and scholarships are given to them.DEO,CDO and other people are invited.These people encourage the people to study well and do good in the scholarship programme.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ranking</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe students obtaining scholarship should maintain their ranks.The help they receive are based according to the improvements they make.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Progress Detail</li>\r\n 	<li>Depending upon the progress in their studies after obtaining the scholarship,the institution or the group that are handing over the scholarship to the students are made available twice a year.\r\n\r\nCriterias for the selection</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Students for Sadbhaw scholarship are selected on the basis of their educational calibre and their financial background.Any student having the chance of obtaining scholarship is based on 75% of their family background and 25% of his/her educational status at present.There are various criterias for the selection of students for sadbhaw scholarship.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Financial condition: The family background of any student obtaining the scholarship and the financial status of the family is rated first.For this type of rating,each local intellectual as well as elite organize a small independent meeting-Sadbhaw meeting is held.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n2.Educational Qualification:For obtaining the Sadbhaw scholarship,the student should be doing well in their previous class.\r\n\r\n3.After obtaining the scholarship,the students with the scholarship must follow the rules and regulations well in order to continue the up coming years.', 'Selection Process', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1826-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-31 04:58:18', '2016-08-31 04:58:18', '', 1826, 'http://localhost/sadbhaw/1826-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
